{"tid":759142,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"撫摸兔仔很重要! 增加自尊心!","createTime":"2018-07-28T10:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T11:03:01.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e81c82691c54c954b9890d29457d0f2b3217d160","tid":759142,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:45:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">在大自然內，兔仔有牠們的等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔仔會groom (舔和梳理) 一個次級(inferior)的兔仔。但高級的亦會要求次級的兔仔groom 牠，這是一定要服從的。當兔仔低頭向前躺在地上，牠就是想你groom (撫摸和親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、令牠舒適、快樂、心理健康。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令牠們冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。<br />\n<br />\n兔仔是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predatory animal)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video是一個等級制度的例子, 可以在0:59 看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c9ddccd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒）：<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f8504693\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>領養兔仔，不要買！</strong></span>🐰🐰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子正在等新主人帶牠們去新的家，過新的生活。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6f9b84d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> <br />\n<br />\n兔子親吻主人，這是代表你是一個好主人，以下2個videos 可看到：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMaovq8Vz1LM&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5cc9bc23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpyL0yEs-ka8&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F149%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=034549a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyL0yEs-ka8</a>"},{"pid":"31a4064d3c106a13c5eced8ab4fd811a3a7cc602","tid":759142,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:47:42.000Z","msg":"我會一路幫佢沖涼一路摸佢，佢好興奮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c763be04a2c1228ba3d4197000e3568ee264bc","tid":759142,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"佢想要就groom佢=低級<br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c62e6043a74a9e8888914b10722ac48b00f17f6","tid":759142,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。 </span>"}]}